    <b>What can I do to help manage the volume of bugmail I receive?</b>
    <p>Every bugmail sent by Malone includes one or more <span style="white-space: nowrap">X-Launchpad-Bug</span>
    headers. You can use tools such
    as <a href="http://www.procmail.org">procmail</a> to create custom filters
    based on this header.</p>

    <a href="https://wiki.launchpad.canonical.com/InitialBugContacts#xlpbug">
      <span style="white-space: nowrap">X-Launchpad-Bug</span> docs
    </a>
